(Combivir) with either efavirenz (Sustiva 600mg qd) as the NNRTI or indinavir-ritonavir (Crixivan/Norvir 800/100mg 
bid) as the ritonavir-boosted protease inhibitor-based regimen.
This patient was randomized to Zidovudine plus Lamivudine (Combivir) and efavirenz group.
On an unknown date, patient developed progressive multifocal leukoencephalopathy.
Action taken with suspect drugs and outcome of the event was unknown. 
Company physician considered the event serious due to important medical event.